CatDescriptText: The picket signs list departments Kaufmann's workers are striking including "Sales Offices, Maintenance, Elevators,  Alterations, Furs, Restaurants, Building Trades, Warehouses, Shoe Service, Engineers".
TitMainTitle: Men walking picket line, two carrying signs that read, "Employees of Kaufmann's Members of A F of L and CIO Unions Are Supporting This Strike"
